    <p>BLOCK: You want a big do? </p>
    <p>Mr. FISCHER: I would just want to be among them, the mass of people who are celebrating and giving high fives. And I'm just thrilled about where we are as a state and how exciting it's going to be to see the next stage of Alaska begin. </p>
