    <p>Ms. MARISSA SKILLINGS: He talks nonstop. </p>
    <p>Mr. ANDREW SKILLINGS: My mother gave this to me as a present. It's a piggy bank. Thing right he measures this table - how come... </p>
    <p>Ms. SKILLINGS: Talking and talking and talking. </p>
