    <p>SIEGEL: And would you assume that Shanahan could turn up coaching another NFL team? </p>
    <p>FATSIS: I think he'll have a job within two or three weeks. He's only 56 years old. We mentioned those three vacancies, and there will be no doubt others coming in the next few weeks, maybe one created even just for Mike Shanahan. </p>
