    <p>FATSIS: I like the rookie quarterbacks this weekend: Matt Ryan of Atlanta, Joe Flacco of Baltimore, the Miami Dolphins under Bill Parcells, great revival. And let's not forget Payton Manning and the Indianapolis Colts; they look pretty good. They won the last nine games of the regular season, and Manning today won his third NFL Most Valuable Player award. </p>
