    <p>(Soundbite of laughter) </p>
    <p>Ms. SCHAAF: It's definitely not, and I actually was just working on my sponsorship packet before we got on the phone here. It's definitely going to take some luck and some help in order to succeed next year. </p>
    <p>BLOCK: You mentioned you were doing a sponsorship packet. </p>
