    <p>M: (Through Translator) Once he stops his attacks, then we will say, OK, Obama is a good president for us.</p>
    <p>REEVES: We head back to Islamabad in Sha's taxi. Soon, we're outside the Marriott Hotel. Four months ago, 56 people died when the hotel was attacked by a suicide truck bomb.</p>
